  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# BMAD Memory Performance Dashboard\n\n**Purpose:** Deep-dive performance monitoring for latency-sensitive operations (hooks, embeddings, context injection).\n\n**Key Metrics:** Hook duration percentiles | Embedding latency | Context injection token counts | Trigger response times\n\n**SLA Targets:** Hooks p95 <500ms | Embeddings p95 <2s | Retrievals p95 <3s\n\n**Documentation:** `/docs/prometheus-queries.md` - See \"Hook Performance Metrics\" and \"Latency Monitoring\" sections"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Memories (with Embeddings)",
      "description": "Total memory entries with embeddings across all V2.0 collections. All memories have dense embeddings (required). If 0, check Qdrant collections exist and contain data.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(bmad_collection_size)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "Total Memories"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "noValue": "No data",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "green"
              },
              {
                "value": 10000,
                "color": "yellow"
              },
              {
                "value": 100000,
                "color": "orange"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Embedding Duration (Avg)",
      "description": "Average embedding generation time. Target: <2s. High values indicate network issues or embedding service overload. Check http://localhost:28080/health if >2s.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(bmad_embedding_duration_seconds_sum) / sum(bmad_embedding_duration_seconds_count)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "Average"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3,
          "noValue": "No data",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "green"
              },
              {
                "value": 1.0,
                "color": "yellow"
              },
              {
                "value": 2.0,
                "color": "red"
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Embedding Duration Over Time",
      "description": "Embedding latency trends by type. Helps identify performance degradation patterns. Spikes indicate temporary network/service issues.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 10,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (embedding_type) (bmad_embedding_duration_seconds_sum) / sum by (embedding_type) (bmad_embedding_duration_seconds_count)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "avg - {{embedding_type}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(bmad_embedding_duration_seconds_sum) / sum(bmad_embedding_duration_seconds_count)",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "avg - all types"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "spanNulls": true,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "pointSize": 5,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "none",
              "group": "A"
            },
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "axisLabel": "Duration",
            "scaleDistribution": {
              "type": "linear"
            },
            "hideFrom": {
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false,
              "legend": false
            },
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line"
            }
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "green"
              },
              {
                "value": 1.0,
                "color": "yellow"
              },
              {
                "value": 2.0,
                "color": "red"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["mean", "max", "last"]
        }
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Embedding Request Activity",
      "description": "Cumulative embedding requests over time (Pushgateway sparse data). Shows total count - steps indicate new requests. Not a per-second rate due to sparse metric updates.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 10,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (embedding_type, status) (bmad_embedding_requests_total)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{embedding_type}} - {{status}}"
