        "w": 24,
        "h": 3
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "---\n\n**Performance Thresholds:** Hook p95 <500ms is critical for user experience - hooks block Claude's workflow. Embedding p95 <2s ensures responsive memory capture. Context injection tokens should stay under 3000 to avoid latency.\n\n**Troubleshooting:** If panels show \"No data\", the system may be idle or newly installed. Trigger activity by using Claude Code normally - hooks will fire and metrics will populate. Check monitoring API health: `curl http://localhost:28000/health`\n\n**Optimization:** High embedding latency? Check network connectivity to embedding service (port 28080). High hook latency? Check Qdrant response times. High token counts? Review memory retrieval relevance scoring."
      }
    }
